'''创世者之眼'''（'''Eye of Brahma'''，'''梵天之眼'''）富有传奇性的黑钻石，相传这颗钻石附有诅咒，原为[[印度|印度]][[本地治里|本地治里]]的[[印度教|印度教]][[梵天|梵天]]神像的眼睛，被一名印度教僧侣摘下，原重195克拉，从此流落在外<ref name=Fanthorpe>[[#Fanthorpe|Fanthorpe, Lionel & Patricia]], p. 203</ref>
<ref name=Harlow>[[#Harlow|Harlow, George E.]], p. 45</ref>。

传说从此之后，这颗黑钻的主人便被诅咒：三位持有人先后跳楼自杀—1932年将这颗钻石进口到美国的纽约珠宝商帕里斯（J. W. Paris）跳樓自殺，與1947年[[俄国|俄国]]公主纳迪亚（Nadia Vyegin-Orlov），李奥妮拉（Leonila Galitzine-Bariatinsky）相隔一个月相继自杀<ref name=tribune>{{Citation  | last = Lavis  | first = Tom  | title = Black Orlov Diamond Reportedly to be Worn by Nominee Huffman During Academy Awards  | work = [[The_Tribune-Democrat|The Tribune-Democrat]]  | publisher = Community Newspaper Holdings  | date = 2 March 2006  | url = http://tribune-democrat.com/local/x519123880/Black-Orlov-Diamond-reportedly-to-be-worn-by-nominee-Huffman-during-Academy-Awards?keyword=secondarystory  | accessdate = 10 June 2011  | archive-date = 2012-04-06  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406120840/http://tribune-democrat.com/local/x519123880/Black-Orlov-Diamond-reportedly-to-be-worn-by-nominee-Huffman-during-Academy-Awards?keyword=secondarystory  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。

後來这颗钻石被切割成三块，辗转被民间收藏家收藏。

